    <div id="rsync">
      <h3>Rsync for mirroring</h3>
      <p>The recommended way for mirroring our ftp server is rsync.</p>
      <ol>
	<li>You should check our packages by the following command.
	  <blockquote>
	    % <code>rsync rsync://rsync.linux-ipv6.org/</code>
	  </blockquote>
	<li>With following command you can mirror our packages.
	  <blockquote>
	    % <code>rsync -rztpvl --delete rsync://rsync.linux-ipv6.org/usagi/ /home/ftp/pub/usagi/</code>
	  </blockquote>
      </ol>
      <p>
	If you establish a new mirror server, please send a mail to 
	<A href="mailto:www-admin@linux-ipv6.org">www-admin@linux-ipv6.org</A>. 
	We'll add your site to our mirror list.
      </p>
